  },
  {
    "id": "fb10885b-da13-4fd4-8a59-edef59220fd9",
    "type": "highlight",
    "bookId": "397",
    "bookTitle": "Mostly Harmless",
    "bookAuthor": "",
    "anchor": 28,
    "offset": 17,
    "length": 266,
    "page": 3,
    "total": 207,
    "text": "All it got was an error message. It tried to look up the error message in its error message look-up table and couldn\u2019t find that either. It allowed a couple of nanoseconds to go by while it went through all this again. Then it woke up its sector function supervisor.",
    "note": "",
    "color": "yellow",
    "created": 1780105658268
  },
  {
    "id": "bcbc0205-49cc-41e4-904f-7240ab75cbb8",
    "type": "highlight",
    "bookId": "432",
    "bookTitle": "The Blade Itself",
    "bookAuthor": "",
    "anchor": 155,
    "offset": 0,
    "length": 472,
    "page": 22,
    "total": 551,
    "text": "\u201cBut after three years, production was up. It was doubled in fact. So you were brought back to Adua, to work under Superior Kalyne. I thought perhaps you would learn discipline with him, but it seems I was wrong. You insist on going your own way.\u201d The Arch Lector frowned up at him. \u201cTo be frank, I think that Kalyne is afraid of you. I think they all are. They don\u2019t like your arrogance, they don\u2019t like your methods, they don\u2019t like your\u2026 special insight into our work.\u201d",
    "note": "",
    "color": "yellow",
    "created": 1780105920668
  },
